{"tid":2515344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前AV女優須藤早貴涉殺夫被捕後 再被揭發欺詐271萬元","createTime":"2021-05-04T02:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T02:19:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"283f6a7bfb236da74a0419bf4e8a55b2785e8e66","tid":2515344,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p6HdEAOQ9R6_dxMy3YJmLT7VylE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZYZFYS46RCQJLD4MGFLJAK3NY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp6HdEAOQ9R6_dxMy3YJmLT7VylE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZYZFYS46RCQJLD4MGFLJAK3NY.jpg&h=0dfdbd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本和歌山縣富豪野崎幸助於2018年5月24日被發現中毒身亡，享年77歲。野崎的25歲前AV女優嫩妻須藤早貴事隔近三年後被捕，她涉嫌為得到13億日圓（約9,300萬港元）遺產而謀殺親夫。除了懷疑殺人和涉毒被捕外，日前再有報道指，須藤於去年6月被揭發欺詐，指她從野崎繼承的公司騙取3,830萬日圓（約271萬港元），而舉報人是公司的前核數師，和歌山警方正在調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n法律文件中，須藤被指於2018年9月從公司的銀行戶口將該筆款項轉帳到其名下的戶口，須藤雖然在野崎死後，成為公司的執行董事，但卻沒有法律效力。須藤於同年7月亦繼承野崎另一間公司成為執行董事。到8月就有報道指野崎在離世前已立好遺囑，將全部遺產捐給田邊市政府。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4LFTsZv5diEKLIca0057GuWAd08=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QOITDZVJ4ZCCFED2XD66GRGZ6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4LFTsZv5diEKLIca0057GuWAd08%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQOITDZVJ4ZCCFED2XD66GRGZ6A.jpg&h=d0033f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/egKxVPFDRgcqjBrdo77AtjSKHBQ=/802x1079/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNFMFUXUB5HRZNF2P7FTXLAKOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FegKxVPFDRgcqjBrdo77AtjSKHBQ%3D%2F802x1079%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNFMFUXUB5HRZNF2P7FTXLAKOE.jpg&h=8443f899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2Hun9W8JA-UH2dei9lWyTA7f6Tg=/802x614/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P46W4UKSERCJDPX767Y27KUDNQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2Hun9W8JA-UH2dei9lWyTA7f6Tg%3D%2F802x614%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP46W4UKSERCJDPX767Y27KUDNQ.JPG&h=7729867e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210504/UO6S55N2UVHB3JM7J2QN22VL2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210504%2FUO6S55N2UVHB3JM7J2QN22VL2I%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=790813e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210504%2FUO6S55N2UVHB3JM7J2QN22VL2I%2F&h=7562a29f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210504/UO6S55N2UVHB3JM7J2QN22VL2I/</a>"},{"pid":"4dc4e8e8012208add49819938f8d8de7f7212dac","tid":2515344,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"又睇av..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}